            "title": "群核上限7.62元定價 1手中籤率3%  暗盤升1.57倍賺5990元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「杭州六小龍」之一的群核科技(00068)公佈，以招股價上限每股7.62元定價，每手500股，一手中籤率僅為3%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"群核科技招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/00068.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"群核科技招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/00068.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">群核科技招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司在港公開發售超額1589.56倍，未有超額重新分配，股份今日（4月17日）正式掛牌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">群核在輝立暗盤收報19.6元，升1.57倍，成交1.81億元，一手賬面賺5990元 ; 富途暗盤報20.52元，較招股價7.62元，飆升1.69倍或12.9元︳一手賬面購6450元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15883037-%e7%be%a4%e6%a0%b8%e4%b8%8a%e9%99%907-62%e5%85%83%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9-1%e6%89%8b%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%a4%e7%8e%873-%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e5%8d%871-57%e5%80%8d%e8%b3%ba5990%e5%85%83",
